comments: Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (ORL) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Ross (ORL) moves alongside of McLaughlin's (MIN) path to the basket and places an arm at his side.  The contact is marginal and does not affect McLaughlin's play at the basket.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Russell (MIN) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Okogie (MIN) swipes down but avoids making contact with Fournier (ORL) during his driving shot attempt.
McLaughlin (MIN) is not in the path of Gordon (ORL) when he sets the screen and continues to back into him to make contact that affects his ability to defend the play.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Russell (MIN) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Gordon (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Russell (MIN).

Fournier (ORL) makes contact to Beasley's (MIN) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.  When Fournier swipes down, he makes contact with the ball and does not dislodge it and then makes contact to the arm when Beasley is still in a shooting motion.
Reid (MIN) makes contact to Gordon's (ORL) body and dislodges him from his position as he has gathers possession of the rebound.
Anthony (ORL) commits a take foul on Vanderbilt (MIN).
